                     <interp inst="t18260622-85-person566" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Fagan, a salesman. I bought two snuff-boxes of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-85-person567">
                  THOMAS 
                  CLEMENTS
